<paragraph id="43D7D65C408C6D5784226783732748B7" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Acker-Knorpelkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="460CED7B83C0404D90D191279A52D24E" pageId="null" pageNumber="760" type="description">
<paragraph id="6808592B994CDF585F93FE79BD6D801D" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="A85FD331D51025CDDA297CF5ED51772A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Polycnemum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="760" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="majus">
<emphasis id="90DCD03A2B9173B4C8FAE9DDEB5109DF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">P. majus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="F0EF099BA8A7B91B0CBAE1685805CCB5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">
<normalizedToken id="68F464E979C9BDC001626043FC56E042" originalValue="Vorblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Vorblaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="71109FD92F9C773975C581D51234F3FF" originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
bis so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="7181D100D7C5941A024B94140376DD55" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="9592805EF53FFEBD90984FE68EDEBEBE" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
1
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="3D9AD4C42AA6FEA4952C2357A43EA319" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">1,5 mm lang. -</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="57B115949F34CBADD348211A92282173" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="72078A5FC469DA7F829E572850C115E8" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">
<emphasis id="0CFF945A279EE5E7559A046CCE8FBC58" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8E84B7BB67F4BD172E4763CD255A8221" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">
<emphasis id="3B382D6F3E612AFF47248915867FB40C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="C56E7FBAC2CBDF22346B1A6E7F49C61B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Polycnemum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="760" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="majus">
<emphasis id="5512A6BABE7A1CAE69998780EF325303" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">P. majus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="66F013D2E94B18B2DE3DBD73AB1B1957" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">
<emphasis id="84FF1D7C64695CBD04583D5251E52CC5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="A49C470EA27F373F81DEE88B47EE49F7" originalValue="Südeuropäisch-südwestasiatische" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">Suedeuropaeisch-suedwestasiatische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="EAE1F26032A93F77061ECDA42867BBDF" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Polycnemum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="760" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="majus">
<emphasis id="B27A2373908836C12313BD4C3C858982" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">P. majus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, jedoch weiter 
<normalizedToken id="F1B22075314B1D9F49FA765AB1F6B3A7" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
(bis Norddeutschland und Baltikum); 
<normalizedToken id="8A8CE2CC829826C2E9A8C57F5B3021DB" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="760">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Westsibirien und zu den zentralasiatischen Gebirgen. - Im Gebiet: Wie vorige Art, jedoch seltener (Verbreitung ist festzustellen).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
